title: Getting Started with Warhammer 40,000
description:
Get a taste for the new edition of Warhammer 40,000 with this awesome video for getting started.

Download the core rules for free here: https://bit.ly/43AMWW5

title: Join the Battle for Oghram – Warhammer 40,000
description: War is coming to Oghram, and you can help to decide the fate of an entire planet! https://bit.ly/43nYVqb

title: Batch Paint: Battle Ready Hive Fleet Leviathan Termagants
description:
Leviathan is the largest of the hive fleets, countless beasts controlled by a synaptic network of terrifying potency. In this video we'll show you how to quickly batch paint your Termagants to a Battle Ready standard in Leviathan's signature colours.

If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it

title: How to Paint: Battle Ready Ultramarines Terminators
description:
Ultramarines are exemplars of martial excellence and discipline, clad in regal gold and blue. Follow this step-by-step guide to get your Ultramarines Terminators painted to a Battle Ready standard, ready to strike down enemies of the Imperium in no time.
        
If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it

title: How to Paint: Battle Ready Tyranid Prime
description:
A Tyranid Prime is a key command organism for the Hive Fleets, relaying the synaptic commands of the Hive Mind. In this guide, we'll be showing you how to paint the Tyranid Prime to Battle Ready, with a few extra steps to take it to the next level.
 
If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it"

description:
